<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; overflow: hidden">
    <canvas id="canvas" style="background: silver"></canvas>
    <div id='path' style="overflow-y: visible;"></div>
    <input type="button" class="data_json" value="Save Data"></input>
    <input type="button" class="clear_canvas" value="Clear"></input>
<div id="mySidenav" class="sidenav">
  <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="closebtn">&times;</a>
  <% if user_signed_in? %>
      <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
      <%= link_to('Logout: '+@me, destroy_user_session_path, method: :delete) %>        
      </div>
    <% end %>
    <select name="users" id="users_all">
    <% @users.each do |user| %>
        <option value=<%= user[:id] %>><%= user[:email] %></option>
    <% end %>
    </select>
    <select name="gestures" id="gesture_all">
        <option value="0">Select Gesture</option>
      <% count=1; @gestures.each do |gesture| %>
        <option data-strokes=<%= gesture[:num_stroke] %> data-count=<%= count %> value=<%= gesture[:id] %>><%= gesture[:name] %></option>
    <%count +=1; end %>
    </select>
    <div><input type="button" class="plot_ges green_btn" value="Plot Data"></div>
    <div><input type="button" class="delete_gesture green_btn" value="Delete Gesture">
    <input type="button" class="delete_gesture_part green_btn" value="Delete Last Execution"></div>
    <div class="desc"></div>
    <input type="file" name="filesToUpload[]" id="filesToUpload" />
    <input id="ispassword" type="checkbox" name="is_password"><label> Is Password Gesture</label><br><br>
    <div><label>Number of Touches: </label>
    <input type="text" id="num_strokes">
    </div>
    <div class="hidden_element" style="visibility: hidden;">
    <div class="1">
        Close: With Index finger parallel to y-axis, open the hand to cover the screen, close the hand around halfway toward the palmâ€™s center.
         <%= image_tag("close.png", {:style => "width:100%;"}) %>
    </div>
    <div class="2">
        FTCW: Put Thumb and Index finger parallel to x-plain, keep thumb fixed, other fingertips rotate around it in a clockwise direction making quarter circle
        <%= image_tag("rotate.png", {:style => "width:100%;"}) %>
    </div>
    <div class="3">
        Bolt fast: Excluding thumb finger, four finger move from top to down forming electric bolt like symbol in fast motion.
        <%= image_tag("bolt.png", {:style => "width:60%;"}) %>
    </div>
    <div class="4">
        Bolt slow: Excluding thumb finger, four finger move from top to down forming electric bolt like symbol in slow motion.
        <%= image_tag("bolt.png", {:style => "width:60%;"}) %>
    </div>
    <div class="5">
        Circle Similar fast: Using one fingers from each hands, two circle are drawn in same direction(clockwise or anti clockwise) in fast motion
        <%= image_tag("circle.png", {:style => "width:100%;"}) %>
    </div>
    <div class="6">
        Circle Similar slow: Using one fingers from each hands, two circle are drawn in same direction(clockwise or anti clockwise) in slow motion
        <%= image_tag("circle.png", {:style => "width:100%;"}) %>
    </div>
    <div class="8">
        Circle different fast: Using one fingers from each hands, two circle are drawn in different direction one clockwise and another anti clockwise in fast motion.
        <%= image_tag("circle.png", {:style => "width:100%;"}) %>
    </div>
    <div class="7">
        Circle different slow: Using one fingers from each hands, two circle are drawn in different direction one clockwise and another anti clockwise in slow motion.
        <%= image_tag("circle.png", {:style => "width:100%;"}) %>
    </div>
    <div class="10">
        I right-left: Using three fingers, cursive "i" like shape is drawn from right to left of the screen
        <%= image_tag("i.png", {:style => "width:100%;"}) %>
    </div>
    <div class="9">
        I left-right: Using three fingers, cursive "i" like shape is drawn from left to right of the screen
        <%= image_tag("i.png", {:style => "width:100%;"}) %>
    </div>
    <div class="11">
        Erase fast: Move two fingers making a "Z" like shape in fast motion
        <%= image_tag("z.png", {:style => "width:100%;"}) %>
    </div>
    <div class="12">
        Erase slow: move two fingers making a "Z" like shape in slow motion
        <%= image_tag("z.png", {:style => "width:100%;"}) %>
    </div>
    <div class="13">
        Dollar S and || : Make dollar sign starting from S and later drawing lines
        <%= image_tag("$.png", {:style => "width:60%;"}) %>
    </div>
    <div class="14">
        Dollar || and S : Make dollar sign starting from lines and later drawing S shape
        <%= image_tag("$.png", {:style => "width:60%;"}) %>
    </div>
</div>
</div>

<!-- Use any element to open the sidenav -->
<span class="open_navslide" >>></span>
</body>
